These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, country
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
City: colone, hannover
2 different pets are kept: fish, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
2. the fan of country is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the fan of funk##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Music-Genre      | funk  | country   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| City         | hannover | colone |
| Pet     | fish | frog    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, lily
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, biathlon
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, cola
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is climbing is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Flower          | tulip     | lily |
| Sport   | biathlon | climbing  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Beverage     | milk   | cola    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, canadian
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
City: venice, hamburg
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the argentine is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Nationality    | canadian     | argentine |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| City         | venice         | hamburg        |
| Hobby   | singing         | card-games    |

