The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, coach
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, scientific
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, pop
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the coach is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the fan of pop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Nationality      | polish     | spanish |
| Job          | coach   | software-developer  |
| Movie-Genre         | horror | scientific     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | pop         |

