There 2 different types of food: broccoli, garlic
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog
1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the fan of folk##1
2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Music-Genre      | folk | house       |
| Color           | pink      | ivory     |
| Food   | garlic       | broccoli   |
| Pet           | frog          | chinchilla |

