.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
House: tower, colonial
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola
2 different pets are kept: cat, horse
There 2 different types of food: orange, grapes
1. the person eating grapes is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
3. the colonial house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| House           | colonial | tower    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea       | cola |
| Pet           | cat         | horse    |
| Food         | orange    | grapes   |

