.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-11::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, ambient
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, basketball
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Music-Genre           | house | ambient |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk      |
| Flower           | amaryllis      | balloon-flower          |
| Sport         | basketball | badminton       |

