.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-12::.
2 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, october
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, oliveros
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
2. the game-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Game         | mah-jongg   | chess |
| Birthday           | november | october    |
| Cigar   | game      | oliveros         |
| Sport         | sailing   | weightlifting |

