.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, skiing
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, japanese
There 2 different types of food: spinach, radish
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the chinese is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Sport         | skiing        | cycling |
| Nationality         | chinese          | japanese     |
| Food   | spinach        | radish     |

 